  <summary date="2023-11-07T11:50:08Z" status="Introduced in House">National Human Trafficking Hotline Enhancement Act

This bill requires an applicant for a grant to operate the National Human Trafficking Hotline to certify that the applicant will provide information received from the hotline to state and local law enforcement agencies, at their request.</summary>
